{"tid":1873674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：你地班no stake廢青中意攬炒丫嘛","createTime":"2020-02-10T18:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T15:53:52.000Z","uid":163154,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6e2e776e4b0ddae1a7855500ae53cfcfb6416972","tid":1873674,"uid":163154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:50:12.000Z","msg":"林鄭：你地班no stake廢青中意攬炒丫嘛，本港女咪順下你地意囉&gt;_O<br />\n<br />\n例子：-<br />\n<br />\n1）特撚登唔封關，你死你事。<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">於本地種植病毒株<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n2）扣起曬你地班賤民既口罩，唔單止扣起唔畀口罩市民，再用海關condom工具截斷一切入口貨源，凍結曬你地成批貨再送畀上面班大劣權貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爽YY <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無口罩你班廢青點撚反朕？點出街？乖乖地無口罩出去奶毒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n3）親自宣揚咪撚戴口罩既精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">加快社區傳播</span><br />\n<br />\n4）哈哈，強制隔離14日，安在家中？靠自律，但照出街，出左咪畀第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、第三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />....第N次警告囉，吹波呀？仲要執「法」者係童軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">加劇社區傳播</span><br />\n<br />\n5）屌，唔小心發夢個陣搞到香港變第二個武漢添，感染人數過多，<br />\n要係夢中<span style=\"color: red;\">封城殺喪屍喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n結論：香港人真係太善良，咁樣既政府到依一刻都未End，即係就算有再多既人死，剩返既人都只會淆底偷生落去，唔會做到堅決推翻到任何野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭呢一步真係<span style=\"color: red;\">真攬炒，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完爆你班口爆式：香港人加油&mdash;&gt;反抗&mdash;&gt;報仇 既no stake廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200208/VS6UUJZG32EVA55LI4BZ5AGQBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2FVS6UUJZG32EVA55LI4BZ5AGQBE%2F&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4aVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=86ca16c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200208%2FVS6UUJZG32EVA55LI4BZ5AGQBE%2F&h=87314cc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200208/VS6UUJZG32EVA55LI4BZ5AGQBE/</a>"},{"pid":"2e1b54c34088d5ee3748cdb59d0a6e48c8030934","tid":1873674,"uid":8014,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:52:11.000Z","msg":"林奠：香港人報仇唔係口號<br />\n<br />\n係行動 佢決定報晒d 仇落香港人到"},{"pid":"ba9caa2c4e59f8cace77ba602ff686f22a448927","tid":1873674,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:53:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27952e0666723026dbbcb27c2b487f385502a864","tid":1873674,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hvcagbp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvcagbp.jpg&h=1e272efd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6B2RJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6B2RJ4.jpg&h=2604c676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StbN2PD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStbN2PD.jpg&h=874d5396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MikryXq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http